
This creates and starts a lxc container from a .ova sdk image.

1. Download LM SDK .ova file.
2. Run this script with the .ova as parameter: 
   sudo ./lm-lxc-sdk.sh ~/Downloads/vm-0.25-swa_system-rnd-20170404-1313.ova
3. Done.

Script will ask for confirmation before proceeding. Old container
will be deleted, so don't leave any valuables inside it.

